Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:12.14,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sharl,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:13.53,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:15.80,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,You really
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:18.49,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,are Heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.62,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We were telling the truth, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:29.37,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Heroes from Biscotti and Galette.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:07.56,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I found our stuff, so we can \Ncommunicate with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:10.15,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it connects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:13.69,DogDays-ep-title,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)\an7}The Dragon Priestess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.69,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:17.95,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This allows us to communicate \Nwith Biscotti and Galette!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:19.86,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:21.62,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:23.23,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.20,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I reached you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.91,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:31.28,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.01,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:34.42,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:36.02,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:39.76,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Princess; we're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.40,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:43.58,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:47.14,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Each of the three countries just \Nsent out search teams for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.32,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.26,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.09,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The south side of the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:55.11,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon Forest on the Corone Plateau.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:56.40,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,So she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.16,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.85,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's surprisingly close.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:03.85,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,If I send out someone now, \Nwe should be able to meet you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:05.56,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:06.89,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:09.05,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right! I have to introduce you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.23,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sharl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:19.07,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, this girl saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.32,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Sharl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.84,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,A Dragon Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.36,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the leader of Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.50,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Millihiore Firianno Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.84,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.17,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku and Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.98,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.09,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,We'll probably be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:44.12,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,getting close to the entrance \Nto the dragon's forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.99,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,We'll likely be intruding \Non everyone there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:50.87,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Um... it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:55.89,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah, I'm safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:57.74,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.38,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.76,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:05.51,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul and the others already \Nwent looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.01,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be on our way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.39,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.84,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad they're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.73,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.72,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:22.07,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we're safe for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.39,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We and Pastillage's high-speed flyers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.29,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,are on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:30.04,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We should see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.66,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.75,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kuu-sama, Becky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.96,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.92,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take the chance to explore
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.46,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,this place before we meet up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:43.84,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.26,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:48.74,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of our two Heroes, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.72,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.38,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:17.12,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,There's only half as much water as normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.90,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's so amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.50,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Do dragons live here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.51,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.98,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.95,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,That is the True Dragon of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.24,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,She controls water and thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:53.62,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.96,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The True Dragons control \Nthe blessings of the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.49,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Water, fire, wind, and greenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.14,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So they're like the land gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.86,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps they're the same to you humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:15.14,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,but to us they're very different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:19.20,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The dragons are the life and \Nnature of this land itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:24.02,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:27.24,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is it normally even more amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:28.30,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.32,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,That's the fire dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:37.66,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It gives energy to the land \Nvia the power of the volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.06,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:01.48,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:07.14,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time, the dragons were thought \Nto be harbingers of natural disasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.90,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,They would cause storms \Nand make volcanoes erupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.74,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But we realized that after the disasters like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.35,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,heavy rains, storms, and volcanic eruptions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:21.11,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,the land would always regain its energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.25,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I think Rico-chan might've \Ntold me that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.71,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that the dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.52,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,restore balance to the scales of nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:32.27,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,and undo the damage caused by \Nhumans and other life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.55,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:36.60,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,And it's the Dragon Priestesses who
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.21,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,connect the dragons and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:41.51,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,She tells us what the dragons are going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:44.32,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,ahead of time, so that we \Ndon't become enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:48.23,DogDays-main,Ku,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes she lends the power \Nof the dragons to arid lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.15,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,So they're amazing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.16,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.28,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That must've been rough \Nfor Shinku and Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.30,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They've both been confirmed as safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:02.07,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll be waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:03.17,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.71,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But the Dragon Forest is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.92,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,a rare place to end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.64,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a good place for them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.55,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,to expand their knowledge as heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.30,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But I've heard something about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.77,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,demon-like creatures appearing there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.56,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:20.56,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,In the dragon's forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:23.26,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze, I'd like you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.81,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,to give me more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:27.88,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.32,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,This is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.14,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the edge of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:43.94,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a lot of humans come here, \Nit won't surprise the dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.87,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,and won't bother anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.80,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here until your people come to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.56,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,So then
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:55.03,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,the things that attacked \Nyou back there were...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.43,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:03.77,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Around the end of summer, \Nthey suddenly appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.23,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,They attack dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.52,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,and hurt the creatures in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.78,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since they appeared, \Nthe dragons have been scared
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:16.03,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,and the land and the plants are going crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.78,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So there are others besides \Nthe one we defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.54,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I keep defeating them and \Nthey keep appearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:27.71,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're being born \Nsomewhere in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:31.10,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,That root is sucking away the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.03,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,life of the forest and the \Npower of the dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.67,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,and using it to create demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:38.04,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find that root and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:41.87,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The dragons always help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:43.76,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Dragon Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.85,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this, I have to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.30,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.61,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Hero's job to fight demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.04,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Dragon Priestess's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:00.49,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for human Heroes to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:03.09,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:04.73,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I always have been,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.25,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,and I always will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.33,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sharl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:17.59,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.85,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,They're angry because one \Nof their kind was slain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.78,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,They're close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.48,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.35,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here, Heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.53,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Dragon Forest's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.32,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave this room. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.02,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.91,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,She's an archer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:57.26,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is that crest magic, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.04,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:30.77,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.02,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.75,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,And we said we would!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.44,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Boomerang Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.78,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.37,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.43,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,There are still so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:59.19,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:13.93,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.44,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage's Sky Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.25,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.57,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:29.83,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.65,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:34.75,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's get rid of those demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.58,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.67,DogDays-main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Knights, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.12,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:58.27,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.61,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all those knights on birds...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.36,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the Pastillage Sky Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.67,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku! Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.37,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:12.37,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.75,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You're Sharl-san, the \NDragon Priestess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.12,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:23.16,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to cause so much noise in \Nthe skies over the dragon forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:25.92,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,but the tri-country alliance \Nof Biscotti, Galette,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:29.01,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,and Pastillage will defeat the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.89,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tri-country alliance? Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.10,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:37.77,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Rico?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.67,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see the Heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.65,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.67,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.28,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Rico! Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.98,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.12,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:59.50,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But no real Galette warrior would
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.60,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,have a problem with these wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:02.39,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.21,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Now here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.88,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's knock them out of the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.59,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Explosive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:16.46,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.63,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul and the Genoise, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:27.23,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody who left to \Nfind you met up midway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:30.45,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,So we can take care of any demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.37,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Hero Shinku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:38.12,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.93,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:43.23,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,rude to the Dragon Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:48.15,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I-I'm sorry! I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.63,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:52.20,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,This was just for safety reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.60,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.14,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.29,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Liscia and the others are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:01.17,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,We probably won't be caught \Noff-guard in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.52,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:06.44,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is that, even if \Nwe defeat the demons here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.59,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,it probably doesn't mean the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.28,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.29,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We've wiped out all the \Ndemons in visible range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.11,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No sign of reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:18.32,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:21.64,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Aria and Lucy will \Ncontinue to search for enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.86,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody else, head down to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:24.78,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:27.47,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We have to greet the Dragon Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:30.31,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.55,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Rico!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.74,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.26,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:40.39,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to worry us, but why \Ndid you make the princess worry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.94,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:44.52,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.52,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.98,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.90,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:58.42,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:01.66,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful for all your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:02.60,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.24,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,We help each other when we're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:08.79,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored to meet you, Dragon Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.12,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Take a drink from these, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.92,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sachi fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:22.85,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.81,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,A crash-landing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.22,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,That must've sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:27.98,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.49,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming to save us, Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:31.77,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.49,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.49,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.14,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.75,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,May we talk to you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:48.19,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm part of Galette's anti-demon squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.02,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,This is Rico...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:53.26,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,A scientist with the Royal Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.64,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about those demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.14,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:02.48,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of a \Ndemon who attacks dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:06.33,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,and who can steal power from
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.02,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,a True Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.65,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried it may be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.78,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,a very dangerous dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:17.77,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,There's a legend passed down among
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.91,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,dragon-users and priestesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.89,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,"When a demon appears that attacks the dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.84,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,a priestess must defeat \Nit with her own blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:28.49,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,That is the job of a priestess who lives
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.72,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,with the dragons and draws from their power."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:36.17,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to give you \Nthe missing Heroes safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:39.05,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:42.20,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Rest tonight and leave early
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.81,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.91,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.60,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.91,DogDays-main,Ga,0000,0000,0000,,It's really close from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.98,DogDays-overlap,E,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.41,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.74,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:17.63,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,the priestess doesn't really \Nknow the details, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:21.14,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't get any good information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.13,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.89,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.27,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But Noir and I did some looking into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.24,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,and the demons we fought
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:32.15,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,are transformed forest creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:35.15,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The real demon must be \Nsomewhere in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.92,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:39.65,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,the damage to the dragons will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:43.00,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Rico, Noir. Smart thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:48.91,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,In regards to the identity of the demon, \Nwe asked an expert about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:53.17,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking into it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:59.28,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. I was enjoying a peaceful day off,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.68,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,and you brought this bothersome work in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.91,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,No complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:06.80,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Our descendants are in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.34,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.68,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,From what you've said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.30,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,it's a demon who feeds off the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.34,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a plant type,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:18.44,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,so if you can find it,\N it should be easy to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:21.28,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But it's concerning that it can
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.20,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,take power from a True Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:25.25,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:28.08,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:31.83,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Hey kid, contact the little one right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.77,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,The Pastillage's elite air-land \Nknights are heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:40.59,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,And ask Galette and Biscotti \Nfor help, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.09,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.13,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.60,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.82,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,A war with a demon army \Nin the dragon's forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:55.23,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, it could \Nthreaten the entire continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.48,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Commando unit, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:00.29,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:04.17,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! This isn't a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.61,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real war against the demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:06.62,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:09.66,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But we do the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.76,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the plan and stay in formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:13.87,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat the enemy that appears \Nwith all your strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.12,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,and protect your allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.25,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:19.94,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti Knights! Camp 1, head out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:26.38,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, our Hero seems to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:29.10,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,have the oddest destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:32.97,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,This time he's fighting demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:35.38,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,with the priestess in the Dragon's Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:36.52,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:39.36,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end of trouble around that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:41.73,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku is a hero, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.11,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:48.57,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,he goes wherever people need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:51.37,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:55.25,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,The tri-country alliance is on its way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:33.56,DogDays-main-top,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting close to another new girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:34.55,DogDays-main-top,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:36.45,DogDays-main-top,M,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:40.09,DogDays-next-ep-title,M,0000,0000,0000,,Big Battle!\NThe Dragon Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:39.64,DogDays-main-top,M,0000,0000,0000,,Valerio-sama! Behind you!
